102
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,480
Titah daripada maharaja.

103
00:03:26,110 --> 00:03:27,620
Meriahnya hari ini.

104
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,130
Menurut titah baginda,

105
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:31,520
Gundik Rong, sila terima titah.

106
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:39,280
Maharaja menitahkan,

107
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:43,200
