-Tak boleh!
-Tak boleh!

114
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,880
Awak cakap dulu.

115
00:04:01,740 --> 00:04:03,890
Sida-sida Li, adakah awak tersilap?

116
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,170
Yan Yiyi tak menghormati atasan

117
00:04:06,410 --> 00:04:08,530
dan pecahkan pasu kesayangan maharaja.

118
00:04:09,090 --> 00:04:11,040
Kenapa dia hanya dikurung

119
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,890
di istana dingin sehari saja?

120
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:14,030
Betul!

121
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,460
Saya hancurkan pasu baginda

122
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:16,870
kepada 1,890 serpihan.

123
00:04:16,870 --> 00:04:18,010
Baginda sepatutnya
kurung saya selama 100 hari.

124
00:04:18,010 --> 00:04:18,820
Betul!

125
00:04:20,210 --> 00:04:22,000
Maharaja menyayangi Gundik Rong.

126
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:23,680
Sebuah pasu bunga saja

127
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:24,820
tak dapat menandingi

128
00:04:25,170 --> 00:04:27,300
perasaan baginda terhadap puan.

129
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,120
(Sanggup pula dia sebut kata-kata
yang menjijikkan.)

130
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,890
(Penipu!)

131
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:34,080
(Apakah muslihat Qin Keji itu?)

132
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,940
(Saya harus cari jalan lain.)

133
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,160
Namun Yan Yiyi langsung tak insaf.

134
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,380
Dia makan makanan mewah

135
00:04:40,380 --> 00:04:42,230
dan berseronok di istana dingin.

136
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,530
Jelas-jelas dia tak pedulikan

137
00:04:43,530 --> 00:04:46,060
hukuman yang dijatuhkan oleh maharaja.

138
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:46,640
Betul.

139
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:48,500
Saya tak pedulikannya.

140
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:50,620
Fikiran dan kelakuan saya tak senonoh,

141
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:52,350
kamu tak boleh bebaskan saya.

142
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:54,740
Hei.

143
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,260
Awak ada alasan apa lagi?

144
00:04:56,260 --> 00:04:57,400
Cepat beritahu saya.

145
00:04:58,530 --> 00:04:59,360
Apa maksud awak?

146
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,480
Awak jangan salah faham.

147
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,290
Kita berada di pihak yang sama sekarang.

148
00:05:03,450 --> 00:05:05,050
Siapa mahu berada di pihak
yang sama dengan awak?

149
00:05:06,180 --> 00:05:07,000
Apa kata

150
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,530
saya pukul awak lagi?

151
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:10,070
Awak tak waras?

152
00:05:10,210 --> 00:05:10,650
Pergi!

153
00:05:11,710 --> 00:05:13,480
Puan berdua jangan bertengkar lagi.

154
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:15,910
Titah maharaja tak boleh diubah.

155
00:05:16,370 --> 00:05:17,720
Kalau tak, puan dianggap
mengingkar titah.

156
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,130
Gundik Rong,

157
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,190
sila ikut hamba keluar.

158
00:05:22,050 --> 00:05:23,950
Biarlah saya mengingkari titah,
saya takkan keluar dari sini.

159
00:05:25,340 --> 00:05:26,330
Kalau begitu,

160
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:29,060
ampunkan hamba.

161
00:05:30,110 --> 00:05:30,770
Awak nak buat apa?

162
00:05:33,510 --> 00:05:38,010
Lepaskan saya, saya tak nak keluar!

163
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:41,090
Kenapa puan buat begini?

164
00:05:41,090 --> 00:05:42,240
Puan pulang ke istana sendiri.

165
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,790
Sana lebih selesa
daripada istana dingin.

166
00:05:44,010 --> 00:05:45,930
Awak tak faham.

167
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:47,550
Hamba memang tak faham.

168
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:50,370
Tarik bersama.

169
00:05:51,590 --> 00:05:54,900
Satu, dua, tiga!

170
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:02,720
(Istana Huaqing)

171
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:05,970
Patik minta tuanku tarik balik titah.

172
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:10,450
Jika orang lain
yang keluar dari istana dingin,

173
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,510
