174
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,200
Kenapa awak langsung

175
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:16,330
tak bersyukur atas niat baik beta?

176
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,830
Patik junjung kasih.

177
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,670
Namun, bukankah patik
melakukan kesalahan berat?

178
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,330
Patik perlu bermuhasabah diri
di dalam istana dingin.

179
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,540
Jika patik dibebaskan sekarang,

180
00:06:22,540 --> 00:06:23,900
patik hanya akan bahayakan rakyat jelata.

181
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,530
Beta ialah maharaja.

182
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:30,700
Beta sentiasa menepati janji,

183
00:06:31,340 --> 00:06:32,700
takkan mengubah titah sesuka hati.

184
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:35,030
Tuanku usir patik ke sana semalam,

185
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:35,760
tapi bebaskan patik hari ini,

186
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:36,830
bukankah itu juga bermaksud ubah titah?

187
00:06:40,890 --> 00:06:41,610
Maksud patik,

188
00:06:41,790 --> 00:06:43,710
apa kata tuanku pertimbangkan lagi?

189
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:47,100
Keputusan beta muktamad.

190
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:48,590
Jika tiada perkara lain,

191
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,430
sila berundur.

192
00:06:49,690 --> 00:06:50,560
Tak boleh.

193
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:51,960
Jika tuanku tak setuju,

194
00:06:52,460 --> 00:06:53,180
patik akan...

195
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:53,620
Patik...

196
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:55,450
Apa yang awak akan buat?

197
00:06:56,650 --> 00:06:56,920
Patik...

198
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,780
Patik akan mati bersamanya.

199
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:11,410
Satu peti berharga sepuluh tahil.

200
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,540
Dalamnya ada enam biji.

201
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:13,690
Jika awak sudi,

202
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,530
silakan.

203
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,440
Awak ada perkara lain lagi?

204
00:07:25,150 --> 00:07:25,480
Baik.

205
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:27,360
Tak mengapa jika tuanku tak setuju.

206
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:31,800
Lagipun sudah lama patik
ingin dapatkan tubuh tuanku.

207
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:34,110
Jika tuanku tak kurung
patik di istana dingin,

208
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:35,580
patik akan beri tuanku minum
ubat penggalak seks setiap hari!

209
00:07:45,530 --> 00:07:46,420
Apa tuanku nak buat?

210
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:54,070
♪Dengar, bunyi pasang surut♪

211
00:07:54,230 --> 00:07:56,260
♪Katanya, saya sudi♪

212
00:07:56,500 --> 00:08:00,840
♪Mentari terbenam merapati awak
